overview: Vladimir Fedoseyev conducts the Moscow Radio Symphony Orchestra in three of Tchaikovsky's masterpieces in a 1991 live performance at the Alte Oper Frankfurt. Works include the Symphony no. 1 in G Minor, op. 13 ("Winter Daydreams"), "Francesca da Rimini," op. 32, and "Variations on a Rococo Theme," op. 33. Antonio Meneses is the cello soloist.
title: The Tchaikovsky Cycle: Vol. 1
